Newcastle is the most rat-infested place in the UK with 5 per cent of residents calling in exterminators last year . 
  London Borough of Southwark has the most mice, cockroaches and bed bugs . 
  Birmingham topped the league table for the highest number of rat exterminations with 15,000 in 2013-14 . 
  Tyneside residents are the most likely to report problems with rats . 
  Wales was the most pest-free place with Southend the least . 
  British Pest Control Association said pests numbers are at their highest for years . 
 